for longevity in animal studies.

00:06:49.370 --> 00:06:52.900 align:middle line:84%
They're living 15%
longer from having this.

00:06:52.900 --> 00:06:55.270 align:middle line:84%
What's going on with
charcoal in general

00:06:55.270 --> 00:06:58.550 align:middle line:84%
