lipopolysaccharide.

00:07:05.620 --> 00:07:07.030 align:middle line:90%
You have gut bacteria.

00:07:07.030 --> 00:07:09.220 align:middle line:84%
All of us have some good
ones and some bad ones,

00:07:09.220 --> 00:07:10.570 align:middle line:90%
